{"tid":1419020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場真係一個好地方","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T23:05:19.000Z","uid":143139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb8261256c5af395e94b078d7ecd11f61660294","tid":1419020,"uid":143139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:01:50.000Z","msg":"每日幾千萬上落<br />\n不如大家多啲去嘆下冷氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668bf7c1aa2f5a033ed6370d1121e139aff4e942","tid":1419020,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:04:22.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"792962bea526937aa871ce7bfd770ce4e14eef93","tid":1419020,"uid":46748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d63f3e786c3cfa51c258ffd3411e633568552744","tid":1419020,"uid":165456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:05:19.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷，輪到和理非出場喇"}]}